features: Liquid Iron Supplements for Men, Women, and Kids: Iron is important for blood production, cellular health, energy metabolism, and overall health. In fact, iron is important for transporting oxygen through the body! Adequate oxygen levels are crucial for good health, and sufficient iron intake helps ensure that you’re getting the oxygen you need.

Blood Builder Iron Supplement: Iron is a critical component of hemoglobin and myoglobin, proteins of red blood cells and muscle cells respectively. Red blood cells — through their relationship with hemoglobin — accept, store, and transport oxygen throughout the body as needed.

Enhanced Absorption: Our iron for women, men, and children ages 4+ comes from bioavailable Ferrochel, otherwise known as ferrous bisglycinate chelate, a unique form of iron that may have higher absorption rates and increased tolerability than iron salts.

Easy-to-Take Liquid: This gentle iron supplement for women, men, and kids comes in liquid form so it’s easy to swallow and adaptable for measuring doses as needed for your family — even when the kiddos need a smaller dose. Suitable for ages 4 and up. Shake well before use. Adults take 1 tablespoon once daily. See dosage chart for further recommendations. Do not exceed the suggested dose.

For Most Lifestyles: MaryRuth's liquid iron supplement for kids and adults is Non-GMO, Vegan, No Artificial Colors. Liquid iron made in a GMP (Good Manufacturing Practice) Facility. Dairy Free, Nut Free, Gluten Free, Soy Free, Sugar Free. B Corp Certified.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works Well and Taste is Bearable
reviews.reviewText: This tastes as good as you can expect drinking iron to taste. I like the raspberry flavor but you can still taste the metallic iron flavor as well. I don't blame the product because even pills I have tried tasted like iron as well as it is a strong flavor. Unfortunately, the iron flavor was a bit more noticeable after this was refrigerated which is necessary after opening it.Still this was a life saver since I had very low iron and don't do well swallowing pills. The liquid makes it easy to get the amount I need and I believe it worked well as far as absorbency goes because my Iron levels were back to normal after I had been taking this for a couple months and rechecked my bloodwork.I'm going to stick with this brand for any vitamins or supplements I need in the future.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My New Favorite Iron
reviews.reviewText: I have been looking for an iron supplement that increases my iron and doesn't taste nasty. I have tried so many different brands. Most make me so nauseous. In my experience, pills are not absorbed well and I have seen little results from them. So, I turned to liquid supplements hoping to increase absorption, but most take disgusting. This one is the most pleasant of all the liquid iron supplements I have taken. It has a pleasant berry flavor and a just a slight noticeable aftertaste. I mix it with just a couple of ounces of apple juice and chase it with a little water. I have been trying to avoid iron infusions and opted to faithfully take this one. My hematologist told me new studies now show taking iron every other day actually gives you better absorption. So, I have been taking this iron for about 6 months and have watched my iron steadily increase, so it is working! I am thrilled. I won't use any other brand.

reviews.reviewText: This product is amazing. I bought it for my husband to help bring his iron levels back up and improve hair fallout. He loves it and prefers it over pills. I am glad there's a product out there like this. Iron is one of many essential minerals needed. This is our second bottle and we will keep purchasing in the future. We also use the multi-vitamin essentials (fruit punch) and the coconut dream. Both are wonderful flavors which maintains the motivation to take it. However, if you don't like Pina coladas you won't like the coconut dream. I'm excited to try their other products and start replacing all the pill bottles with Mary Ruth. :)
